c: 7
v: 22
t: "Tokkel usuk Yallal keenih abe xiibal ken duquurusak taaqat aracak ken oobiseh, tokkel usun woo caxak tammoyseeniih yokmen waqdi ken Qawrat keenih yumbullech jannatti cooxih caffa sinnit kafsaanam Qembisen, ken Rabbi keenih seeceeh, Anu woo caxah makmok sin mawaasinniyoo? diggah sheytan sin nımmayak Qaduwwiy Qadaawat kak baxxaqqa iyye siinik maxaccinniyoo? keenik iyye"